```plantuml
@startuml ShiftLeftSecurity_traceleft

actor User

participant "CLI" as CLI
participant "TextProcessor" as TextProcessor
participant "SysInteraction" as SysInteraction
participant "CLITools" as CLITools

User -> CLI: Start Command
CLI -> CLITools: Initialize Command
CLITools -> CLI: Command Ready

note over CLI: Command can be Unicode processing or System interaction

alt Unicode Normalization
    CLI -> TextProcessor: Normalize Unicode Text
    TextProcessor -> TextProcessor: Perform NFC/NFD/NFKC/NFKD
    TextProcessor -> CLI: Return Normalized Text
end

alt Collation
    CLI -> TextProcessor: Compare Strings
    TextProcessor -> TextProcessor: Use CLDR Tables
    TextProcessor -> CLI: Return Comparison Result
end

alt System Interaction
    CLI -> SysInteraction: Perform System Call
    SysInteraction -> SysInteraction: Access OS API
    SysInteraction -> CLI: Return System Call Result
end

User -> CLI: Command Result

@enduml
```